  "prompt": "Should I send a Facebook friend request to ex bf?",
  "response": "That depends on several factors:\n\n1. How long ago did the relationship end?\n2. How did the relationship end?\n3. Are you both emotionally over the breakup?\n4. Would reconnecting potentially cause drama or emotional stress?\n5. Are you currently in another relationship?\n\nGenerally, sending a friend request to an ex can be complicated and might:\n- Reopen old emotional wounds\n- Create misunderstandings\n- Interfere with moving on\n- Cause tension with current partners\n\nConsider carefully whether this is a good idea for your emotional well-being.",
